text:
The Animal Crossing Sanrio Collaboration Pack amiibo cards are available starting today! Use them with Animal Crossing: New Horizons and bring some Sanrio cuteness to your island.

Invite special residents to your campsite and help them relocate permanently, then pick up themed items based on characters like Hello Kitty, Cinnamaroll and more!

Available exclusively at Target!
